<h2 class="bac">Qualifications:</h2>
<p class="bac">
The ideal MBA candidate must demonstrate strong leadership, influence, analytic and communication skills, as well as exhibit strong personal commitment and motivation, with the ability to drive execution at both the team and individual level. He/she must be able to present ideas and opinions openly and honestly, even when they oppose prevailing opinions and practices. Effectively communicate and influence in a global, virtual environment across Bank of America, and within each line of business. Must possess strong organizational and time management skills, with an ability to prioritize and manage multiple activities simultaneously. Candidates must have completed a Bachelor&#39;s degree in Business, Engineering or other technical major, with three to five years of previous work experience. Candidates must be eligible to work in the US.
</p>

